arge;\">即時進行雙真普選<br />\n由民選政府組織獨立調查委員會徹查</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n如果由777政府組織獨立調查委員會<br />\n即係自已人查自已人  搵笨！<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.playsport.cc/upload/forum/14902389098846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.playsport.cc%2Fupload%2Fforum%2F14902389098846.jpg&h=8d241555&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a2b85cbeae07047952aa05baeb29630a6aedc28","tid":1540164,"uid":269498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:00:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>繼續燃燒</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"019ae99156824ce87841653aca5bb1bed7e4a630","tid":1540164,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f28d5efc73816a8da34c3ce5a8c17de5d81f56fd","tid":1540164,"uid":261343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"又話唔可以撤回？<br />\n你叫班藍絲同黑警支持左你咁耐令到自己神憎鬼厭係為左咩野？<br />\n原來有暴徒先會聽市民講野<br />\n但我唔想每一次都要抗爭政府先會聽我講野<br />\n所以寫左係基本法既雙普選係一定要有！<br />\n若果之前話唔可以撤回呢家又變可以既話<br />\n咁即係其餘四大訴求都應該可以由做唔到變到做到喇<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:00:15.000Z","msg":"你依段可以做民宣"},{"pid":"45a143d88abefa8432119bcc90b18e951a96b716","tid":1540164,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"019ae99156824ce87841653aca5bb1bed7e4a630","tid":1540164,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f28d5efc73816a8da34c3ce5a8c17de5d81f56fd","tid":1540164,"uid":261343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"又話唔可以撤回？<br />\n你叫班藍絲同黑警支持左你咁耐令到自己神憎鬼厭係為左咩野？<br />\n原來有暴徒先會聽市民講野<br />\n但我唔想每一次都要抗爭政府先會聽我講野<br />\n所以寫左係基本法既雙普選係一定要有！<br />\n若果之前話唔可以撤回呢家又變可以既話<br />\n咁即係其餘四大訴求都應該可以由做唔到變到做到喇<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:00:15.000Z","msg":"你依段可以做民宣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:00:47.000Z","msg":"我it唔得<br />\n揾人幫手整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7861c97f63a03f3451bbb1e8b944a7923b1be2ee","tid":1540164,"uid":21572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:01:49.000Z","msg":"準備定9月8上街"},{"pid":"28436fda4c0302def50925eab0c0407a7005e876","tid":1540164,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:01:54.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 屌你老母民陣！9.8 通過人權法大遊行由維園去美領！快申請不反對通知書！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dOKFzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dOKFzS</a>"},{"pid":"ffeafc6d55f5898e70c709a117a08cd29edd3587","tid":1540164,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:03:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8C114.NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.371869629957626%210503649999998&amp;z=10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8C114.NTs%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.371869629957626%25210503649999998%26z%3D10&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=126d7bdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8C114.NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.371869629957626%210503649999998&amp;z=10</a><br />\n<br />\n全面抵制藍色餐廳<br />\n打經濟戰啊要"},{"pid":"dfe9dcd3f3fa12497c3ffa7cf42bb94fb060233f","tid":1540164,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案、<br />\n臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\">清朝債主權問題</span><br />\n</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n#1down4togo<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港、洗腦教育\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">流水革命</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"465c7ea6cc5b3226b77f1c4fcbc43635d2df9cec","tid":1540164,"uid":30115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:03:44.000Z","msg":"9月8 一片美國旗海"},{"pid":"67eebcaeebba4a6802798fd2d8b5d5d340fa3ba3","tid":1540164,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:03:49.000Z","msg":"On9,識少少機械都知，大火林小小水係會更大火"},{"pid":"8031098a05d7aea7fdbb53d4fa715f86d5d2d617","tid":1540164,"uid":70679,"like":0,"disl